{"tid":2129461,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本30年前舊報紙「預言」 2020年全球一半人染病","createTime":"2020-07-28T15:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T04:51:15.000Z","uid":267658,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d65d2d7f3b75ad2c8d99bab4334f220a0f246104","tid":2129461,"uid":267658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1831309/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC30%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E8%88%8A%E5%A0%B1%E7%B4%99-%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%80-2020%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E4%BA%BA%E6%9F%93%E7%97%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1831309%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC30%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E8%2588%258A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25B4%2599-%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25A8%2580-2020%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%258D%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2597%2585&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD8IAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=387fca4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1831309%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC30%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E8%2588%258A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25B4%2599-%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25A8%2580-2020%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%258D%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2597%2585&h=ea343ff6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1831309/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC30%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E8%88%8A%E5%A0%B1%E7%B4%99-%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%80-2020%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E4%BA%BA%E6%9F%93%E7%97%85</a><br />\n<br />\n日本30年前舊報紙「預言」 2020年全球一半人染病<br />\n2020-07-28 17:03<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/09d85b891cee3845b2a79ded31fff09c/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200728/_2020072817091199258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F09d85b891cee3845b2a79ded31fff09c%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200728%2F_2020072817091199258.jpg&h=53d68263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本30年前舊報紙預測2020半數人類染疫。網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎持續在各地擴大，全球累計確診人數攀升至1650萬例，造成至少65萬人染疫喪命，疫情最為慘重的美國、巴西以及印度，境內確診數都已飆破數百萬例。近日有日本網民翻出日本傳媒30年前出版的報紙，發現當時早已預言2020年將有一場大災難，且其中的許多細節都符合現今情況。<br />\n<br />\n根據《岐阜新聞》於1990年5月2日的報道中指出，世界衞生組織針對全球暖化災害預測發表一份報告，內容提及全球暖化將會造成瘧疾等傳染病大流行，「2020年有一半的人類會感染傳染病」；此外，報告中還提到，假如臭氧層的破洞仍持續擴大，將可能造成人類免疫力低下。<br />\n<br />\n這份報紙中出現許多關鍵字，包含「2020年」、「傳染病」以及「免疫力低下」，都符合現今在全球肆虐的新冠肺炎疫情，儘管目前確診病例未及全球人口的半數，不過疫情範圍仍持續在擴大當中，已對200多個國家造成嚴重影響，這也讓網民形容「真的說中了」、「簡直是神預言！」<br />\n<br />\n不過，《岐阜新聞》事後對此回應，雖然這則報道與今年的疫情和局勢有部分「關鍵字」吻合，但其實在細節方面並不相同，望民眾還是多將焦點放在正在變化的時事上。"},{"pid":"c74bbc597c94a731d21dfd82694105029b3dbcd9","tid":2129461,"uid":292789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d65d2d7f3b75ad2c8d99bab4334f220a0f246104","tid":2129461,"uid":267658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1831309/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC30%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E8%88%8A%E5%A0%B1%E7%B4%99-%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%80-2020%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E4%BA%BA%E6%9F%93%E7%97%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1831309%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC30%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E8%2588%258A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25B4%2599-%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25A8%2580-2020%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%258D%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2597%2585&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD8IAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=387fca4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https